body_html.single: Rustic links adorn a unisex bracelet. 1-100 jewelry gives an organic feel while maintaining an understated elegance. Varying chain-links. Hook-and-eye closure. Color Silver. 100% Sterling Silver. Made in U.S.A. From Hook to Eye Length 7 & 1/2", Size Large. Hook to Eye Length 6", Size Small. Shop our collection of 1-100.
